    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Perhaps, but the way that the initially proposed fix made all `@interact` widgets look really broken is a good illustration of what I mean about each fix introducing other bugs. I know that one is now taken care of, but we don't have long to find out what else this fix might break.\n\nI consider manually creating HBox containers to be a fairly advanced feature, so I don't think it's a big deal if it looks off when 3.0 goes out. I presume you can work around it by setting attributes on the widgets inside it.\n"
